## Auth conventions (confirmed)

- Register returns `{ email, role }` only — no token; clients login separately
- Login: unknown email / wrong password → `"Invalid email or password."`; inactive account → `"Account is inactive."`
- Email verification deferred — keep auth flow simple for now
